== Kwakira ==
Umusesenguzi w’ubuvanganzo Monica Popescu yasobanuye ko ''Boetie Gaan Border Toe'' hamwe ''n’uruhererekane rwarwo, Boetie Op Maneuvers'', nk'ibikorwa byerekanaga urukundo rw’intambara yo ku mupaka wa [[Afurika y’Epfo|Afurika]] y'Epfo kandi byibanze cyane ku "myitwarire idahwitse y'abasirikare ba SADF".  Keyan Tomaselli wo muri kaminuza ya Johannesburg yanenze iyi filime "kwamamaza".
